quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  7,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  7,1,Alif meeem saaad
  7,2,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) yeh kitaab ( jo ) tum par nazil hui hai. is se tumhe tang dil nahi hona chahiye, ( yeh nazil ) is liye ( hui hai ) ke tum is ke zariye se ( logon ) ko dar sunaaoo aur ( yeh ) imaan walon ke liye nasiyaat hai"
  7,3,( logo ) jo ( kitaab ) tum par tumahray perwar-digaar ke haan nazil hui hai is ki pairwi karo aur is ke siwa aur rfiqon ki pairwi nah karo ( aur ) tum kam hi nasiyaat qubool karte ho
  7,4,aur kitni hi bastiyan hain ke hum ne tabah kar dalain jin par hamara azaab ( ya to raat ko ) aata tha jabkay woh sotay they ya ( din ko ) jab woh qelola ( yani dopehar ko aaraam ) karte they
  7,5,to jis waqt un par azaab aata tha un ke munh se yahi nikalta tha ke ( haae ) hum ( haae ) hum ( apne oopar ) zulm karte rahay
  7,6,to jin logon ki taraf paighambar beje gay hum un se bhi prssh karen ge aur payghambaroon se bhi poucheen ge
  7,7,phir apne ilm se un ke halaat bayan karen ge aur hum kahin gayab to nahi they
  7,8,aur is roz ( aamaal ka ) talna barhaq hai to jin logon ke ( amlon ke ) wazan bhaari hon ge woh to nijaat panay walay hain
  7,9,aur jin ke wazan halkay hon ge to yahi log hain jinhon ne apne tain khasaray mein dala is liye ke hamari ayaton ke baray mein be insafi karte they
  7,10,aur hum hi ne zameen mein tumhara thikana banaya aur is mein tumahray liye samaan mashit peda kiye. ( magar ) tum kam hi shukar karte ho
  7,11,aur hum hi ne tum ko ( ibtida mein matti se ) pedakiya phir tumhari soorat shakal banai phir firshton ko hukum diya aadam ke agay sajda karo to ( sab ne ) sajdakiya lekin iblees ke woh sajda karne walon mein ( shaamil ) nah howa
  7,12,( khuda ne ) farmaya jab mein ne tujh ko hukum diya to kis cheez ne tujhe sajda karne se baz rakha. is ne kaha ke mein is se afizal hon. mujhe to ne aag se pedakiya hai aur usay matti se banaya hai
  7,13,farmaya to ( bahisht se ) utar ja tujhe Shayaan nahi ke yahan ghuroor kere pas nikal ja. to zaleel hai
  7,14,is ne kaha ke mujhe is din taq mohlat ataa farma jis din log ( qabron se ) uthaye jayen ge
  7,15,farmaya ( acha ) tujh ko mohlat di jati hai
  7,16,( phir ) shetan ne kaha mujhe to too ne maloonkiya hi hai mein bhi tairay seedhay raste par un ( ko gumraah karne ) ke liye bhethon ga
  7,17,phir un ke agay se aur peechay se dayen se aur baen se ( gharz har taraf se ) aon ga ( aur un ki raah maroo ga ) aur to un mein aksar ko shukar guzaar nahi paye ga
  7,18,"( khuda ne ) farmaya, nikal ja. yahan se pajee. mardood jo log un mein se teri pairwi karen ge mein ( un ko aur tujh ko jahannum mein daal kar ) tum sab se jahannum ko bhar dun ga"
  7,19,aur hum ne aadam ( se kaha ke ) tum aur tumhari biwi bahisht mein raho saho aur jahan se chaho ( aur jo chaho ) nosh jaan karo magar is darakht ke paas nah jao warna gunehgaar ho jao ge
  7,20,to shetan dono ko behkanay laga taakay un ki sattar ki cheezein jo un se posheeda theen khol day aur kehnay laga ke tum ko tumahray perwar-digaar ne is darakht se sirf is liye manakiya hai ke ke tum farishtay nah ban jao ya hamesha jeetay nah raho
  7,21,aur un se qasam kha kar kaha mein to tumhara kher khuwa hon
  7,22,gharz ( mardood ne ) dhoka day kar un ko ( masiat ki taraf ) khech hi liya jab unhon ne is darakht ( ke phal ) ko kha liya to un ki sattar ki cheezein khil gayeen aur woh bahisht ke ( darakhton ke ) pattay toar toar kar apne oopar chipkanay lagey aur ( sattar chupaney lagey ) tab un ke perwar-digaar ne un ko puraka kekiya mein ne tum ko is darakht ( ke paas jaane ) se mana nahikiya tha aur jta nahi diya tha ke shetan tumhara khullam khula dushman hai
  7,23,dono arz karne lagey ke perwar-digaar hum ne apni jaanun par zulmkiya aur agar to hamein nahi bakhshay ga aur hum par reham nahi kere ga to hum tabah ho jayen ge
  7,24,( khuda ne ) farmaya ( tum sab bahisht se ) utar jao ( ab se ) tum aik dosray ke dushman ho aur tumahray liye aik waqt ( khaas ) taq zameen par thikana aur ( zindagi ka ) samaan ( kar diya gaya ) hai
  7,25,( yani ) farmaya ke isi mein tumhara jeena hoga aur isi mein marna aur isi mein se ( qayamat ko zindah kar ke ) nikalay jao ge
  7,26,ae nabi aadam hum ne tum par poshak utari ke tumhara sattar dhanke aur ( tumahray badan ko ) zeenat ( day ) aur ( jo ) parhaiz gari ka libaas ( hai ) woh sab se acha hai. yeh khuda ki nishanain hain taakay log nasihat pakar yn
  7,27,ae nabi aadam ( dekhna kahin ) shetan tumhe b_hka nah day jis terhan tumahray maa baap ko ( b_hka kar ) bahisht se nikalwa diya aur un se un ke kapray utarwa diye taakay un ke sattar un ko khol kar dikha day. woh aur is ke bhai tum ko aisi jagah se dekhte rahay hain jahan se tum un ko nahi dekh satke hum ne shaitano ko inhen logon ka Rafeeq car banaya hai jo imaan nahi rakhtay
  7,28,aur jab koi be hiyai ka kaam karte hain to kehte hain ke hum ne apne buzurgon ko isi terhan karte dekha hai aur khuda ne bhi hum ko yahi hukum diya hai. keh do khuda be hiyai ke kaam karne ka hargiz hukum nahi deta. bhala tum khuda ki nisbat aisi baat kyun kehte ho jis ka tumhe ilm nahi
  7,29,keh do ke mere perwar-digaar ne to insaaf karne ka hukum diya hai. aur yeh ke har namaz ke waqt seedha ( qble ki taraf ) rukhkiya karo aur khaas isi ki ibadat karo aur isi ko poukaro. is ne jis terhan tum ko ibtida mein pedakiya tha isi terhan tum phir peda hogay
  7,30,aik fareeq ko to is ne hadaayat di aur aik fareeq par gumraahi saabit hochuki. un logon ne khuda ko chore kar shaitano ko Rafeeq bana liya aur samajte ( yeh ) hain ke hadaayat yab hain
  7,31,ae nabi aadam! har namaz ke waqt apne tain muzayyankiya karo aur khao aur پیؤ aur be ja nah urrao ke khuda be ja urane walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  7,32,pucho to ke jo zeenat ( vaaraysh ) aur khanay ( peenay ) ki pakeeza cheezein khuda ne apne bundon ke liye peda ki hain un ko haraam kis nekiya hai? keh do ke yeh cheezein duniya ki zindagi mein imaan walon ke liye hain aur qayamat ke din khaas un hi ka hissa hon gi. isi terhan khuda apni ayatain samajhney walon ke liye khol khol kar bayan farmata hai
  7,33,keh do ke mere perwar-digaar ne to be hiyai ki baton ko zahir hon ya posheeda aur gunah ko aur na-haq zayad-ti karne ko haraamkiya hai. aur is ko bhi ke tum kisi ko khuda ka shareek banaao jis ki is ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki aur is ko bhi ke khuda ke baray mein aisi baatein kaho jin ka tumhe kuch ilm nahi
  7,34,aur har aik firqay ke liye ( mout ka ) aik waqt muqarrar hai. jab woh aa jata hai to nah to aik gharri der kar saktay hain nah jaldi
  7,35,ae nabi aadam! ( hum tum ko yeh nasiyaat hamesha karte rahay hain ke ) jab hamaray paighambar tumahray paas aaya karen aur hamari ayatain tum ko sunaya karen ( to un par imaan laya karo ) ke jo shakhs ( un par imaan laa kar khuda se ) darta rahay ga aur apni haalat durust rakhay ga to aisay logon ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  7,36,aur jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya aur un se sartabi ki wohi dozakhi hain ke hamesha is mein ( jaltay ) rahen ge
  7,37,to is se ziyada zalim kon hai jo khuda par jhoot bandhay ya is ki ayaton ko jhutlaye. un ko un ke naseeb ka likha milta hi rahay ga yahan taq ke jab un ke paas hamaray beje hue ( farishtay ) jaan nikaalte ayen ge to kahin ge ke jin ko tum khuda ke siwa puraka karte they woh ( ab ) kahan hain? woh kahin ge ( maloom nahi ) ke woh hum se ( kahan ) gayab hogaye aur iqraar karen ge ke be shak woh kafir they
  7,38,to khuda farmaiye ga ke junoo aur insanon ki jo jamaten tum se pehlay ho guzri hain un ke sath tum bhi daakhil jahannum ho jao. jab aik jamaat ( wahan ) ja daakhil ho gayi to apni ( mazhabi ) behan ( yani apne jaisi doosri jamaat ) par laanat kere gi. yahan taq ke jab sab is mein daakhil ho jayen ge to pichli jamaat pehli ki nisbat kahe gi ke ae perwar-digaar! un hi logon ne hum ko gumraahkiya tha to un ko aatish jahannum ka dugna azaab day. khuda farmaiye ga ke ( tum ) sab ko dugna ( azaab diya jaye ga ) magar tum nahi jantay
  7,39,aur pehli jamaat pichli jamaat se kahe gi ke tum ko hum par kuch bhi fazeelat nah hui to jo ( amal ) tumkiya karte they is ke badlay mein azaab ke mazay chako
  7,40,jin logon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya aur un se sartabi ki. un ke liye nah aasman ke darwazay khole jayen ge aur nah woh bahisht mein daakhil hon ge. yahan taq ke oont soi ke nakay mein se nah nikal jaye aur gunahgaaron ko hum aisi hi saza diya karte hain
  7,41,aisay logon ke liye ( neechay ) bichona bhi ( aatish ) jahannum ka hoga aur oopar se odhna bhi ( isi ka ) aur zaalmon ko hum aisi hi saza diya karte hain
  7,42,aur jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay aur hum ( amlon ke liye ) kisi shakhs ko is ki taaqat se ziyada takleef nahi dete. aisay hi log ahal bahisht hain ( ke ) is mein hamesha rahen ge
  7,43,aur jo kinay un ke dilon mein hon ge hum sab nikaal dalain ge. un ke mehloon ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hon gi aur kahin ge ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne hum ko yahan ka rasta dekhaya aur agar khuda hum ko rasta nah dekhata to hum rasta nah pa satke. be shak hamara perwar-digaar ke rasool haq baat le kar aeye they aur ( is roz ) munhaadi kar di jaye gi ke tum un aamaal ke siilay mein jo duniya mein karte they is bahisht ke waris bana diye gay ho
  7,44,aur ahal bahisht dozakhiyon se pukaar kar kahin ge ke jo wada hamaray perwar-digaar ne hum sekiya tha hum ne to usay sacha pa liya. bhala jo wada tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum sekiya tha tum ne bhi usay sacha paaya? woh kahin ge haan to ( is waqt ) un mein aik pukarnay wala pukare ga ke be insafon par khuda ki laanat
  7,45,jo khuda ki raah se roktay aur is mein kajji dhoondtay aur akhirat se inkaar karte they
  7,46,un dono ( yani bahisht aur dozakh ) ke darmain ( airaaf naam ) aik deewar ho gi aur airaaf par kuch aadmi hon ge jo sab ko un ki sooraton se pehchan len ge. to woh ahal bahisht ko pukaar kar kahin ge ke tum par salamti ho. yeh log bhi bahisht mein daakhil to nahi hon ge magar umeed rakhtay hon ge
  7,47,aur jab un ki nigehain palat kar ahal dozakh ki taraf jayen gi to arz karen ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko zalim logon ke sath shaamil nah kejio
  7,48,aur ahal airaaf ( kafir ) logon ko jinhein un ki sooraton se shanakht karte hon ge pukaarain ge aur kahin ge ( ke aaj ) nah to tumhari jamaat hi tumahray kuch kaam aayi aur nah tumhara taqqabur ( hi soodmand howa )
  7,49,( phir mominon ki taraf ishara kar ke kahin ge )kiya yeh wohi log hain jin ke baray mein tum kasmain khaya karte they ke khuda apni rehmat se un ki dastgeeri nahi kere ga ( to momino ) tum bahisht mein daakhil ho jao tumhe kuch khauf nahi aur nah tum ko kuch ranj o andoh hoga
  7,50,aur woh dozakhi bahishtion se ( girgira kar ) kahin ge ke kisi qader hum par pani bahao ya jo rizaq khuda ne tumhe inayat farmaya hai un mein se ( kuch hamein bhi do ) woh jawab den ge ke khuda ne bahisht ka pani aur rizaq kafiroon par haraam kar diya hai
  7,51,jinhon ne apne deen ko tamasha aur khail bana rakha tha aur duniya ki zindagi ne un ko dhokay mein daal rakha tha. to jis terhan yeh log is din ke anay ko bhoolay hue aur hamari ayaton se munhkir ho rahay they. isi terhan aaj hum bhi inhen bhala den ge
  7,52,aur hum ne un ke paas kitaab pouncha di hai jis ko ilm o danish ke sath khol khol kar bayan kar diya hai ( aur ) woh momin logon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  7,53,kiya yeh log is ke wadahazaab ke munhtazir hain. jis din woh wada aajay ga to jo log is ko pehlay se bhoolay hue hon ge woh bol utheen ge ke be shak hamaray perwar-digaar ke rasool haq le kar aeye they. bhala ( aaj ) hamara koi sfarshi hain ke hamari sifarish karen ya hum ( duniya mein ) phir lota diye jayen ke jo amal ( bad ) hum ( pehlay ) karte they ( woh nah karen balkay ) un ke siwa aur ( naik ) amal karen. be shak un logon ne apna nuqsaankiya aur jo kuch yeh iftirakiya karte they un se sab jata raha
  7,54,kuch shak nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar khuda hi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay din mein pedakiya phir arsh par ja thehra. wohi raat ko din ka libaas pehnata hai ke woh is ke peechay dorta chala aata hai. aur isi ne Sooraj aur chaand sitaron ko pedakiya sab is ke hukum ke mutabiq kaam mein lagey hue hain. dekho sab makhlooq bhi isi ki hai aur hukum bhi ( isi ka hai ). yeh khuda rab alameen barri barket wala hai
  7,55,( logo ) apne perwar-digaar se aajzi se aur chupkay chupkay duayen manga karo. woh hadd se bherne walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  7,56,aur malik mein islaah ke baad kharabi nah karna aur khuda se khauf karte hue aur umeed rakh kar duayen mangte rehna. kuch shak nahi ke khuda ki rehmat neki karne walon se qareeb hai
  7,57,aur wohi to hai jo apni rehmat ( yani meinh ) se pehlay hawaon ko khushkhabri ( bana kar ) bhejta hai. yahan taq ke jab woh bhaari bhaari baadalon ko utha latayen hai to hum is ko aik meri hui bastii ki taraf haank dete hain. phir baadal semeinh barastee hain. phirmeinh se har terhan ke phal peda karte hain. isi terhan hum mardon ko ( zameen se ) zindah karkay bahar nikaal len ge. ( yeh ayaat is liye bayan ki jati hain ) taakay tum nasiyaat pakro
  7,58,jo zameen pakeeza ( hai ) is mein se sabza bhi perwar-digaar ke hukum se ( nafees hi ) nikalta hai aur jo kharab hai is mein jo kuch hai naaqis hota hai. isi terhan hum ayaton ko shukar guzar logon ke liye phair phair kar bayan karte hain
  7,59,hum ne Nooh ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja to unhon ne ( un se kaha ) ae meri baradri ke logo khuda ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. mujhe tumahray baray mein barray din ke azaab ka ( bohat hi ) dar hai
  7,60,to jo un ki qoum mein sardar they woh kehnay lagey ke hum tumhe Sarih gumraahi mein ( mubtala ) dekhte hain
  7,61,unhon ne kaha ae qoum mujh mein kisi terhan ki gumraahi nahi hai balkay mein perwar-digaar aalam ka paighambar hon
  7,62,tumhe apne perwar-digaar ke pegham pohanchata hon aur tumhari khirkhwahi karta hon aur mujh ko khuda ki taraf se aisi baatein maloom hain jin se tum be khabar ho
  7,63,kiya tum ko is baat se taajjub howa hai ke tum mein se 1 shakhs ke haath tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas nasiyaat aayi taakay woh tum ko dry aur taakay tum parhaizgaar bano aur taakay tum par rehamkiya jaye
  7,64,magar un logon ne un ki takzieeb ki. to hum ne Nooh ko aur jo un ke sath kashti mein sawaar they un ko to bacha liya aur jin logon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya tha inhen ghark kar diya. kuch shak nahi ke woh andhay log they
  7,65,aur ( isi terhan ) qoum Aad ki taraf un ke bhai Hood ko bheja. unhon ne kaha ke bhaio khuda hi ki ibadat karo. is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi.kiya tum drtay nahi ?
  7,66,to un ki qoum ke sardar jo kafir they kehnay lagey ke tum hamein ahmaq nazar atay ho aur hum tumhe jhoota khayaal karte hain
  7,67,unhon ne kaha ke bhaio mujh mein hamaqat ki koi baat nahi hai balkay mein rab alameen ka paighambar hon
  7,68,mein tumhe khuda ke pegham pohanchata hon aur tumhara amanat daar khair khwah hon
  7,69,kiya tum ko is baat se taajjub howa hai ke tum mein se 1 shakhs ke haath tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas nasiyaat aayi taakay woh tumhe dry aur yaad karo to karo jab is ne tum ko qoum Nooh ke baad sardar banaya. aur tum ko phelao ziyada diya. pas khuda ki nematon ko yaad karo. taakay nijaat haasil karo
  7,70,woh kehnay lagey ke tum hamaray paas is liye aeye ho ke hum akailey khuda hi ki ibadat karen. aur jin ko hamaray baap dada pujte chalay aeye hain un ko chore den? to agar sachey ho to jis cheez se hamein darate ho usay le aao
  7,71,Hood ne kaha tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par azaab aur ghazab ka ( nazil hona ) muqarrar ho chuka hai.kiya tum mujh se aisay naamon ke baray mein jhagarte ho jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne ( apni taraf se ) rakh liye hain. jin ki khuda ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki. to tum bhi intzaar karo mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon
  7,72,phir hum ne Hood ko aur jo log un ke sath they un ko nijaat bakhsh aur jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya tha un ki jarr kaat di aur woh imaan laane walay they hi nahi
  7,73,aur qoum smod ki taraf un ke bhai Saleh ko bheja. ( to ) Saleh ne kaha ke ae qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se aik moujza aa chuka hai. ( yani ) yahi khuda ki oontni tumahray liye moujza hai. to usay ( azad ) chore do ke khuda ki zameen mein chrti phiray aur tum usay buri niyat se haath bhi nah lagana. warna azabِ alim mein tumhe pakar le ga
  7,74,aur yaad to karo jab is ne tum ko qoum Aad ke baad sardar banaya aur zameen par abadkiya ke naram zameen se ( matti le le kar ) mehal taamer karte ho aur pahoron ko taraash taraash kar ghar banatay ho. pas khuda ki nematon ko yaad karo aur zameen mein fasaad nah karte phiro
  7,75,to un ki qoum mein sardar log jo ghuroor rakhtay they ghareeb logon se jo un mein se imaan le aeye they kehnay lagey bhala tum yaqeen karte ho ke Saleh apne perwar-digaar ki taraf beje gay hain? unhon ne kaha haan jo cheez day kar woh beje gay hain hum is par bilashuba imaan rakhtay hain
  7,76,to sardaran maghrour kehnay lagey ke jis cheez par tum imaan laaye ho hum to is ko nahi mantay
  7,77,aakhir unhon ne اontnai ( ki konchon ) ko kaat dala aur apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se sar kashi ki aur kehnay lagey ke Saleh ! jis cheez se tum hamein darate they agar tum ( khuda ke ) paighambar ho to usay hum par le aao
  7,78,to un ko bhonchal ne aa pakra aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre reh gay
  7,79,phir Saleh un se ( na umeed ho kar ) phiray aur kaha ke meri qoum! mein ne tum ko khuda ka pegham pouncha diya aur tumhari kher khawahi ki magar tum ( aisay ho ke ) kher khuwahon ko dost hi nahi rakhtay
  7,80,aur isi terhan jab hum ne Loot ko ( paighambar bana kar bheja to ) is waqt unhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke tum aisi be hiyai ka kaam kyun karte ho ke tum se ahal aalam mein se kisi ne is terhan ka kaam nahikiya
  7,81,yani khwahish nafsaani poora karne ke liye aurton ko chore kar londo par girtay ho. haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum log hadd se nikal jaane walay ho
  7,82,to un se is ka jawab kuch nah ban para aur bolay to yeh bolay ke un logon ( yani Loot aur is ke ghar walon ) ko apne gaon se nikaal do ( ke ) yeh log pak ban-na chahtay hain
  7,83,to hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko bacha liya magar un ki bi bi ( nah bachi ) ke woh peechay rehne walon mein thi
  7,84,aur hum ne un par ( patharon ka )meinh barsaya. so dekh lau ke gunahgaaron ka kaisa injaam howa
  7,85,aur mudin ki taraf un ke bhai Shoiab ko bheja. ( to ) unhon ne kaha ke qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani aa chuki hai to tum naap toal poorikiya karo aur logon ko cheezein kam nah diya karo. aur zameen mein islaah ke baad kharabi nah karo. agar tum sahib imaan ho to samajh lau ke yeh baat tumahray haq mein behtar hai
  7,86,aur har raste par mat betha karo ke jo shakhs khuda par imaan nahi lata hai usay tum darate aur raah khuda se roktay aur is mein kajji dhoondtay ho aur ( is waqt ko ) yaad karo jab tum thoray se they to khuda ne tum ko jamaat kaseer kar diya aur dekh lau ke kharabi karne walon ka injaam kaisa howa
  7,87,aur agar tum mein se aik jamaat meri risalat par imaan le aayi hai aur aik jamaat imaan nahi layi hai. aur aik jamaat imaan nahi layi. to sabr kiye raho yahan taq ke khuda hamaray tumahray darmain faisla kar day aur woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai
  7,88,"( to ) un ki qoum mein jo log sardar aur barray aadmi they, woh kehnay lagey ke Shoiab ! ( ya to ) hum tum ko aur jo log tumahray sath imaan laaye hain, un ko apne shehar se nikaal den ge. ya tum hamaray mazhab mein aajao. unhon ne kaha khuwa hum ( tumahray deen se ) bezaar hi hon ( to bhi? )"
  7,89,agar hum is ke baad ke khuda hamein is se nijaat bakhash chuka hai tumahray mazhab mein lout jayen to be shak hum ne khuda par jhoot iftira baandha. aur hamein Shayaan nahi ke hum is mein lout jayen haan khuda jo hamara perwar-digaar hai woh chahay to ( hum majaboor hain ). hamaray perwar-digaar ka ilm har cheez par ihata kiye hue hai. hamara khuda hi par bharosa hai. ae perwar-digaar hum mein aur hamari qoum mein insaaf ke sath faisla kardey aur to sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai
  7,90,"aur un ki qoum mein se sardar log jo kafir they, kehnay lagey ( bhaio ) agar tum ne Shoiab ki pairwi ki to be shak tum khasaray mein prhgye"
  7,91,to un ko bhonchal ne aapkrha aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre reh gay
  7,92,( yeh log ) jinhon ne Shoiab ki takzieeb ki thi aisay barbaad hue they ke goya woh un mein kabhi abad hi nahi hue they ( gharz ) jinhon ne Shoiab ko jhatlaya woh khasaray mein prhgye
  7,93,to Shoiab un mein se nikal aeye aur kaha ke bhaio mein ne tum ko apne perwar-digaar ke pegham pouncha diye hain aur tumhari khirkhwahi ki thi. to mein kafiroon par ( azaab nazil honay se ) ranj vghm kyun karoon
  7,94,aur hum ne kisi shehar mein koi paighambar nahi bheja magar wahan ke rehne walon ko ( jo imaan nah laaye ) dukhoon aur musibaton mein mubtalakiya taakay woh aajzi aur zaari karen
  7,95,phir hum ne takleef ko aasoudgi se badal diya yahan taq ke ( maal واولاد mein ) ziyada hogaye to kehnay lagey ke is terhan ka ranj o rahat hamaray barron ko bhi pohanchana raha hai to hum ne un ko nagahan pkrhlya aur woh ( apne haal mein ) be khabar they
  7,96,agar un bustiyon ke log imaan le atay aur parhaizgaar ho jatay. to hum un par aasman aur zameen ki Barkaat ( ke darwazay ) khol dete magar unhon ne to takzieeb ki. so un ke aamaal ki saza mein hum ne un ko pakar liya
  7,97,kiya bustiyon ke rehne walay is se be khauf hain ke un par hamara azaab raat ko waqay ho aur woh ( be khabar ) so rahay hon
  7,98,aurkiya ehley shehar is se nidar hain ke un par hamara azaab din charrhey aa nazil ho aur woh khail rahay hon
  7,99,kiya yeh log khuda ke dao ka dar nahi rakhtay ( sun lau ke ) khuda ke dao se wohi log nidar hotay hain jo khasara panay walay hain
  7,100,"kiya un logon ko jo ehley zameen ke ( mrjane ke ) baad zameen ke maalik hotay hain, yeh amar mojab hadaayat nahi howa ke agar hum chahain to un ke gunaaho ke sabab un par museebat daal den. aur un ke dilon par mohar lgadin ke kuch sun hi nah saken"
  7,101,yeh bastiyan hain jin ke kuch halaat hum tum ko sunaate hain. aur un ke paas un ke paighambar nishanain le kar aeye. magar woh aisay nahi they ke jis cheez ko pehlay jhutla chuke hon usay maan len isi terhan khuda kafiroon ke dilon par mohar laga deta hai
  7,102,aur hum ne un mein se aksaron mein ( ehad ka nibaah ) nahi dekha. aur un mein aksaron ko ( dekha to ) badkaar hi dekha
  7,103,phir un ( payghambaroon ) ke baad hum ne moose ko nishanain day kar firaon aur is ke اعیان saltanat ke paas bheja to unhon ne un ke sath kufarkiya. so dekh lau ke kharabi karne walon ka injaamkiya howa
  7,104,aur moose ne kaha ke ae firaon mein rab alameen ka paighambar hon
  7,105,mujh par wajib hai ke khuda ki taraf se jo kuch kahoon sach hi kahoon. mein tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani le kar aaya hon. so bani Israel ko mere sath jaane ki rukhsat day degiye
  7,106,firaon ne kaha agar tum nishani le kar aeye ho to agar sachey ho to lao ( dikhao )
  7,107,moose ne apni laathi ( zameen par ) daal di to woh isi waqt Sarih asdeha ( hogaya )
  7,108,aur apna haath bahar nikala to isi dam dekhnay walon ki nigahon mein safaid Buraq ( tha )
  7,109,to qoum firaon mein jo sardar they woh kehnay lagey ke yeh bara allama jadugar hai
  7,110,is ka iradah yeh hai ke tum ko tumahray malik se nikaal day. bhala tumharikiya Salah hai ?
  7,111,unhon ne ( firaon se ) kaha ke fi al haal moose aur is ke bhai ke muamlay ko maaf rakhiye aur shehron mein naqeeb rawana kar degiye
  7,112,ke tamam maahirgado garon ko aap ke paas le ayen
  7,113,( chunancha aisa hikiya gaya ) aur jadugar firaon ke paas aa Pehncahy aur kehnay lagey ke agar hum jeet gay to hamein sila ataakiya jaye
  7,114,( firaon ne ) kaha haan ( zaroor ) aur ( is ke ilawa ) tum muqarabon mein daakhil karliye jao ge
  7,115,( jab fariqain rozِ muqarara par jama hue to ) gado garonne kaha ke moose ya to tum ( jaadoo ki cheez ) daalo ya hum daaltay hain
  7,116,( moose ne ) kaha tum hi daalo. jab unhon ne ( jaadoo ki cheezein ) dalain to logon ki aankhon par jaadoo kardiya ( yani nzrbndi kar di ) aur ( lathyon aur rassiyon ke saanp bana bana kar ) inhen dara diya aur bohat bara jaadoo dekhaya
  7,117,( is waqt ) hum ne moose ki taraf wahi bhaije ke tum bhi apni laathi daal do. woh foran ( saanp ban kar ) gado garonke banaye hue saanpon ko ( aik aik karkay ) nigal jaye gi
  7,118,"( phir ) to haq saabit hogaya aur jo kuch fravni karte they, baatil hogaya"
  7,119,aur woh maghloob hogaye aur zaleel hokar reh gay
  7,120,( yeh kefiyat dekh kar ) jadugar sjday mein gir parre
  7,121,aur kehnay lagey ke hum Jahan ke perwar-digaar par imaan laaye
  7,122,yani moose aur Haroon ke perwar-digaar par
  7,123,firaon ne kaha ke peshtar is ke ke mein tumhe ijazat dun tum is par imaan le aeye? be shak yeh fraib hai jo tum ne mil kar shehar meinkiya hai taakay ehley shehar ko yahan se nikaal do. so anqareeb ( is ka nateeja ) maloom karlo ge
  7,124,mein ( pehlay to ) tumahray aik taraf ke haath aur doosri taraf ke paon ktwa dun ga phir tum sab ko suli chrhhwa dun ga
  7,125,woh bolay ke hum to apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
  7,126,aur is ke siwa tujh ko hamari kon si baat buri lagi hai ke jab hamaray perwar-digaar ki nishanain hamaray paas agaien to hum un par imaan le aeye. ae perwar-digaar hum par sabro istaqamat ke dhanay khol day aur hamein ( mario to ) musalman hi mario
  7,127,aur qomِ firaon mein jo sardar they kehnay lagey kekiya aap moose aur is ki qoum ko chore degiye ga ke malik mein kharabi karen aur aap se aur aap ke mabodon se dast kash ho jaien. woh bolay ke hum un ke larkoon ko qatal krdalin ge aur larkiyon ko zindah rehne den ge aur be shak hum un par ghalib hain
  7,128,moose ne apni qoum se kaha ke khuda se madad mango aur saabit qadam raho. zameen to khuda ki hai. woh apne bundon mein se jisay chahta hai is ka maalik banata hai. aur aakhir bhala to darny walon ka hai
  7,129,woh bolay ke tumahray anay se pehlay bhi hum ko azeeyaten pahunchti rahen aur anay ke baad bhi. moose ne kaha ke qareeb hai ke tumhara perwar-digaar tumahray dushman ko halaak kardey aur is ki jagah tumhe zameen mein khalifa banaye phir dekhe ke tum kaisay amal karte ho
  7,130,aur hum ne firounion ko kehton aur mewoon ke nuqsaan mein pakra taakay nasiyaat haasil karen
  7,131,to jab un ko asayish haasil hoti to kehte ke hum is ke mustahiq hain. aur agar sakhti pahunchti to moose aur un ke rfiqon ki bdshgoni batatay. dekho un ki bdshgoni khuda ke haan muqarrar hai lekin un mein aksar nahi jantay
  7,132,aur kehnay lagey ke tum hamaray paas ( khuwa ) koi hi nishani lao taakay is se hum par jaadoo karo. magar hum tum par imaan laane walay nahi hain
  7,133,to hum ne un par tufaan aur tidiyan aur joyen aur maindak aur khoon kitni khuli hui nishanain bhejen. magar woh taqqabur hi karte rahay aur woh log they hi gunehgaar
  7,134,aur jab un par azaab waqay hota to kehte ke moose hamaray liye apne perwar-digaar se dua karo. jaissa is ne tum se ehad kar rakha hai. agar tum hum se azaab ko taall do ge to hum tum par imaan bhi le ayen ge aur bani Israel ko bhi tumahray sath jaane ( ki ijazat ) den ge
  7,135,phir jab hum aik muddat ke liye jis taq un ko pohanchna tha un se azaab daur kardete to woh ehad ko toar daaltay
  7,136,to hum ne un se badla le kar hi chorra ke un ko darya mein duubo diya is liye ke woh hamari ayaton ko jutlatay aur un se be parwai karte they
  7,137,aur jo log kamzor samjhay jatay they un ko zameen ( shaam ) ke mashriq o maghrib ka jis mein hum ne barket di thi waris kardiya aur bani Israel ke baray mein un ke sabr ki wajah se tumahray perwar-digaar ka wadahnaik poora howa aur firaon aur qoum firaon jo ( mehal ) banatay aur ( angoor ke baagh ) jo chatriyon par charhatay they sab ko hum ne tabah kardiya
  7,138,aur hum ne bani Israel ko darya ke paar utaara to woh aisay logon ke paas ja puhanche jo apne buton ( ki ibadat ) ke liye baithy rehtay they. ( bani Israel ) kehnay lagey ke moose jaisay un logon ke mabood hain. hamaray liye bhi aik mabood bana do. moose ne kaha ke tum barray hi jaahil log ho
  7,139,yeh log jis ( shugal ) mein ( phansay hue ) hain woh barbaad honay wala hai aur jo kaam yeh karte hain sab behooda hain
  7,140,( aur yeh bhi ) kaha ke bhala mein khuda ke siwa tumahray liye koi aur mabood talaash karoon halaank is ne tum ko tamam ahal aalam par fazeelat bakhsh hai
  7,141,( aur hamaray un ehsaanon ko yaad karo ) jab hum ne tum ko firounion ( ke haath ) se nijaat bakhsh woh log tum ko bara dukh dete they. tumahray beton ko qatal kar daaltay they aur baityon ko zindah rehne dete they. aur is mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se sakht azmaish thi
  7,142,aur hum ne moose se tees raat ki meyaad muqarrar ki. aur is das ( raatain ) aur mila kar usay poora ( chilla ) kardiya to is ke perwar-digaar ki chalees raat ki meyaad poori hogayi. aur moose ne apne bhai Haroon se kaha ke mere ( Koh tor par jaane ke ) baad tum meri qoum mein mere janasheen ho ( un ki ) islaah karte rehna theek aur shariron ke raste nah chalna
  7,143,aur jab moose hamaray muqarrar kiye hue waqt par ( koh tor ) par puhanche aur un ke perwar-digaar ne un se kalaamkiya to kehnay lagey ke ae perwar-digaar mujhe ( jalva ) dikha ke mein tera deedar ( bhi ) daikhon. perwar-digaar ne kaha ke tum mujhe hargiz nah dekh sakuu ge. haan pahar ki taraf dekhte raho agar yeh apni jagah qaim raha to tum mujhe dekh sakuu ge. jab un ka perwar-digaar pahar par namodaar howa to ( tajallii anwaar Rabbani ) ne is ko rezah rezah kardiya aur moose be hosh ho kar gir parre. jab hosh mein aeye to kehnay lagey ke teri zaat pak hai aur mein tairay huzoor tauba karta hon aur jo imaan laane walay hain un mein sab se awwal hon
  7,144,( khuda ne ) farmaya moose mein ne tum ko apne pegham aur apne kalaam se logon se mumtazkiya hai. to jo mein ne tum ko ataakiya hai usay pakar rakho aur ( mera ) shukar baja lao
  7,145,aur hum ne ( torat ) ki tkhtyon mein un ke liye har qisam ki nasiyaat aur har cheez ki tafseel likh di phir ( irshad farmaya ke ) usay zor se pakdae raho aur apni qoum se bhi keh do ke un baton ko jo is mein ( mndrj hain aur ) bohat behtar hain pakdae rahen. mein anqareeb tum ko nafarman logon ka ghar dukhao ga
  7,146,jo log zameen mein na-haq ghuroor karte hain un ko apni ayaton se phair dun ga. agar yeh sab nishanain bhi dekh len tab bhi un par imaan nah layein aur agar raasti ka rasta dekhen to usay ( apna ) rasta nah banayen. aur agar gumraahi ki raah dekhen to usay rasta banalen. yeh is liye ke unhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhatlaya aur un se ghaflat karte rahay
  7,147,aur jin logon ne hamari ayaton aur akhirat ke anay ko jhatlaya un ke aamaal zaya ho jaien ge. yeh jaisay amal karte hain waisa hi un ko badla miley ga
  7,148,aur qoum moose ne moose ke baad apne zewar ka aik bitchrha bana liya ( woh ) aik jism ( tha ) jis mein se bail ki aawaz nikalti thi. un logon ne yeh nah dekha ke woh nah un se baat karsaktha hai aur nah un ko rasta dikha sakta hai. is ko unhon ne ( mabood ) bnalya aur ( apne haq mein ) zulmkiya
  7,149,aur jab woh nadim hue aur dekha ke gumraah hogaye hain to kehnay lagey ke agar hamara perwar-digaar hum par reham nahi kere ga aur hum ko maaf nahi farmaiye ga to hum barbaad ho jaien ge
  7,150,aur jab moose apni qoum mein nihayat ghusse aur afsos ki haalat mein wapas aeye. to kehnay lagey ke tum ne mere baad bohat hi bdatwari ki.kiya tum ne apne perwar-digaar ka hukum ( yani mera apne paas aana ) jald chaha ( yeh kaha ) aur ( shiddat ghazab se torat ki ) tkhtyan daal den aur apne bhai ke sir ( ke balon ) ko pakar kar apni taraf khenchnay lagey. unhon ne kaha ke bhai jaan log to mujhe kamzor samajte they aur qareeb tha ke qatal kar dein. to aisa kaam nah kiijiye ke dushman mujh par hansen aur mujhe zalim logon mein mat milaiyay
  7,151,tab unhon ne dua ki ke ae mere perwar-digaar mujhe aur mere bhai ko maaf farma aur hamein apni rehmat mein daakhil kar to sab se barh kar reham karne wala hai
  7,152,( khuda ne farmaya ke ) jin logon ne bichhre ko ( mabood ) bana liya tha un par perwar-digaar ka ghazab waqay hoga aur duniya ki zindagi mein zillat ( naseeb hogi ) aur hum iftira prdazon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  7,153,aur jinhon ne buray kaam kiye phir is ke baad tauba karli aur imaan le aeye to kuch shak nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar is ke baad ( bakhash day ga ke woh ) bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  7,154,aur jab moose ka gussa faro howa to ( torat ) ki tkhtyan athalin aur jo kuch un mein likha tha woh un logon ke liye jo apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain. hadaayat aur rehmat thi
  7,155,aur moose ne is meyaad par jo hum ne muqarrar ki thi apni qoum ke sattar aadmi munhtakhib ( karkay koh tor par haazir ) tal kiye. jab un ko zalzalay ne pakra to moose ne kaha ke ae perwar-digaar to chahta to un ko aur mujh ko pehlay hi se halaak kar deta.kiya to is feal ki saza mein jo hum mein se be aqal logon nekiya hai hamein halaak kardey ga. yeh to teri azmaish hai. is se to jis ko chahay gumraah kere aur jis ko chahay hadaayat bakhshay. to hi hamara karsaaz hai to hamein ( hamaray gunah ) bakhash day aur hum par reham farma aur to sab se behtar bakhsnay wala hai
  7,156,aur hamaray liye is duniya mein bhi bhalai likh day aur akhirat mein bhi. hum teri taraf rujoo ho chukay. farmaya ke jo mera azaab hai usay to jis par chahta hon nazil karta hon aur jo meri rehmat hai woh har cheez ko shaamil hai. mein is ko un logon ke liye likh dun ga jo parhaiz gari karte aur zakaat dete aur hamari ayaton par imaan rakhtay hain
  7,157,woh jo ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) rasool ( allah ) ki jo nabi ammi hain pairwi karte hain jin ( ke Awsaf ) ko woh apne haan torat aur injeel mein likha howa paate hain. woh inhen naik kaam ka hukum dete hain aur buray kaam se roktay hain. aur pak cheezon ko un ke liye halal karte hain aur napak cheezon ko un par haraam t_hrate hain aur un par se boojh aur taoq jo un ( ke sir ) par ( aur gilaay mein ) they utaartay hain. to jo log un par imaan laaye aur un ki rafaqat ki aur inhen madad di. aur jo noor un ke sath nazil howa hai is ki pairwi ki. wohi morad panay walay hain
  7,158,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) keh do ke logo mein tum sab ki taraf khuda ka bheja howa ( yani is ka rasool ) hon. ( woh ) jo asmano aur zameen ka badshah hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi wohi zindagani bakhshta hai aur wohi mout deta hai. to khuda par aur is ke rasool paighambar ammi par jo khuda par aur is ke tamam kalaam par imaan rakhtay hain imaan lao aur un ki pairwi karo taakay hadaayat pao
  7,159,aur qoum moose mein kuch log aisay bhi hain jo haq ka rasta batatay aur isi ke sath insaaf karte hain
  7,160,aur hum ne un ko ( yani bani Israel ko ) allag allag karkay baara qabeeley ( aur ) barri barri jamaten bana diya. aur jab moose se un ki qoum ne pani talabkiya to hum ne un ki taraf wahi bhaije ke apni laathi pathar par maar do. to is mein se baara chashmay phoot niklay. aur sab logon ne apna apna ghaat maloom karliya. aur hum ne un ( ke suron ) par baadal ko saibaan banaye rakha aur un par mann o salewa utaartay rahay. aur ( un se kaha ke ) jo pakeeza cheezein hum tumhe dete hain inhen khao. aur un logon ne hamara kuch nuqsaan nahikiya balkay ( jo ) nuqsaankiya apna hikiya
  7,161,aur ( yaad karo ) jab un se kaha gaya ke is shehar mein sukoonat ikhtiyar karlo aur is mein jahan se jee chahay khana ( piinaa ) aur ( haan shehar mein jana to ) hittah kehna aur darwazay mein daakhil hona to sajda karna. hum tumahray gunah maaf kar dein ge. aur neki karne walon ko aur ziyada den ge
  7,162,magar jo un mein zalim they unhon ne is lafz ko jis ka un ko hukum diya gaya tha badal kar is ki jagah aur lafz kehna shurukiya to hum ne un par aasman se azaab bheja is liye ke zulm karte they
  7,163,aur un se is gaon ka haal to pucho jab lab darya waqay tha. jab yeh log haftay ke din ke baray mein hadd se tajawaz karne lagey ( yani ) is waqt ke un ke haftay ke din machhliyan un ke samnay pani ke oopar aatin aur jab haftay ka din nah hota to nah aatin. isi terhan hum un logon ko un ki nafarmaniyon ke sabab azmaish mein daalnay lagey
  7,164,aur jab un mein se aik jamaat ne kaha ke tum aisay logon ko kyun nasiyaat karte ho jin ko allah halaak karne wala ya sakht azaab dainay wala hai to unhon ne kaha is liye ke tumahray perwar-digaar ke samnay moazrat kar saken aur ajab nahi ke woh parhaiz gari ikhtiyar karen
  7,165,jab unhon ne un baton ko faramosh kardiya jin ki un ko nasiyaat ki gayi thi to jo log buraiee se mana karte they un ko hum ne nijaat di aur jo zulm karte they un ko buray azaab mein pakar liya ke nafarmani kiye jatay they
  7,166,gharz jin aamaal ( bad ) se un ko manakiya gaya tha jab woh un ( par israr aur hamaray hukum se ) gardan kashi karne lagey to hum ne un ko hukum diya ke zaleel bandar hojao
  7,167,( aur is waqt ko yaad karo ) jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne ( yahood ko ) aagah kardiya tha ke woh un par qayamat taq aisay shakhs ko musallat rakhay ga jo inhen buri buri takleifein deta rahay. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar jald azaab karne wala hai aur woh bakhsnay wala meharban bhi hai
  7,168,"aur hum ne un ko jamaat jamaat karkay malik mein munhtashir kar diya. baaz un mein se nekokaar hain aur baaz aur terhan ke ( yani badkaar ) aur hum aasayshon, tklifon ( dono ) se un ki azmaish karte rahay taakay ( hamari taraf ) rujoo karen"
  7,169,phir un ke baad nakhlf un ke qaim maqam hue jo kitaab ke waris banay. yeh ( be tamil ) is dunyae Danni ka maal o mata'ale letay hain aur kehte hain ke hum bakhash diye jayen ge. aur ( log aison par ta'an karte hain ) agar un ke samnay bhi waisa hi maal ajata hai to woh bhi usay le letay hain.kiya un se kitaab ki nisbat ehad nahi liya gaya ke khuda par sach ke siwa aur kuch nahi kahin ge. aur jo kuch is ( kitaab ) mein hai is ko unhon ne parh bhi liya hai. aur akhirat ka ghar parhaiz garon ke liye behtar haikiya tum samajte nahi
  7,170,aur jo log kitaab ko mazboot pakdae hue hain aur namaz ka iltazam rakhtay hain ( un ko hum ajar den ge ke ) hum naiko karon ka ajar zaya nahi karte
  7,171,aur jab hum ne un ( ke suron ) par pahar utha kharakiya goya woh saibaan tha aur unhon ne khayaalkiya ke woh un par girta hai to ( hum ne kaha ke ) jo hum ne tumhe diya hai usay zor se pakdae raho. aur jo is mein likha hai is par amal karo taakay bach jao
  7,172,aur jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne bani aadam se yani un ki pithon se un ki aulaad nikaali to un se khud un ke muqablay mein iqraar kara liya ( yani un se poocha ke )kiya tumhara perwar-digaar nahi hon. woh kehnay lagey kyun nahi hum gawah hain ( ke to hamara perwar-digaar hai ). yeh iqraar is liye karaya tha ke qayamat ke din ( kahin yun nah ) kehnay lagu ke hum ko to is ki khabar hi nah thi
  7,173,ya yeh ( nah ) kaho ke shirk to pehlay hamaray barron nekiya tha. aur hum to un ki aulaad they ( jo ) un ke baad ( peda hue ). tokiya jo kaam ahal baatil karte rahay is ke badlay to hamein halaak karta hai
  7,174,aur isi terhan hum ( apni ) ayatain khol khol kar bayan karte hain taakay yeh rujoo karen
  7,175,aur un ko is shakhs ka haal parh kar suna do jis ko hum ne apni ayatain ataa farmaen ( aur haft parcha ٴ ilm shar'aa )se muzayyankiya ) to is ne un ko utaar diya phir shetan is ke peechay laga to woh gumrahon mein hogaya
  7,176,aur agar hum chahtay to un ayaton se is ( ke darjay ) ko buland kar dete magar woh to pasti ki taraf mael hogaya aur apni khwahish ke peechay chal para. to is ki misaal kuttay ki si hogayi ke agar sakhti karo to zabaan nikalay rahay aur yuhin chore do to bhi zabaan nikalay rahay. yahi misaal un logon ki hai jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya to un se yeh qissa bayan kardo. taakay woh fikar karen
  7,177,jin logon ne hamari ayaton ki takzieeb ki un ki misaal buri hai aur unhon ne nuqsaan (kiya to ) apna hikiya
  7,178,jis ko khuda hadaayat day wohi raah yab hai aur jis ko gumraah kere to aisay hi log nuqsaan uthany walay hain
  7,179,aur hum ne bohat se jin aur ensaan dozakh ke liye peda kiye hain. un ke dil hain lekin un se samajte nahi aur un ki ankhen hain magar un se dekhte nahi aur un ke kaan hain par un se suntay nahi. yeh log bilkul charpayon ki terhan hain balkay un se bhi bhatkay hue. yahi woh hain jo ghaflat mein parre hue hain
  7,180,aur khuda ke sab naam achay hi achay hain. to is ko is ke naamon se puraka karo aur jo log is ke naamon mein kajji ikhtiyar karte hain un ko chore do. woh jo kuch kar rahay hain anqareeb is ki saza payen ge
  7,181,aur hamari makhloqaat mein se aik woh log hain jo haq ka rasta batatay hain aur isi ke sath insaaf karte hain
  7,182,aur jin logon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya un ko batadreej is tareeq se pakren ge ke un ko maloom hi nah hoga
  7,183,aur mein un ko mohlat diye jata hon meri tadbeer ( barri ) mazboot hai
  7,184,kiya unhon ne ghhor nahikiya ke un ke Rafeeq Mohammad ( ) ko ( kisi terhan ka bhi ) junoon nahi hai. woh to zahir zahuur dar sunanay walay hain
  7,185,kiya unhon ne aasman aur zameen ki badshahat mein jo cheezein khuda ne peda ki hain un par nazar nahi ki aur is baat par ( khayaal nahikiya ) ke ajab nahi un ( ki mout ) ka waqt nazdeek poanch gaya ho. to is ke baad woh aur kis baat par imaan layein ge
  7,186,jis shakhs ko khuda gumraah kere is ko koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi aur woh un ( gumrahon ) ko chhorey rakhta hai ke apni sar kashi mein parre behektey rahen
  7,187,( yeh log ) tum se qayamat ke baray mein puchhte hain ke is ke waqay honay ka waqt kab hai. keh do ke is ka ilm to mere perwar-digaar hi ko hai. wohi usay is ke waqt par zahir kardey ga. woh aasman o zameen mein aik bhaari baat hogi aur nagahan tum par aajay gi. yeh tum se is terhan daryaft karte hain ke goya tum is se bakhoobi waaqif ho. kaho ke is ka ilm to khuda hi ko hai lekin aksar log yeh nahi jantay
  7,188,keh do ke mein apne faiday aur nuqsaan ka kuch bhi ikhtiyar nahi rakhta magar jo allah chahay aur agar mein ghaib ki baatein jaanta hota to bohat se faiday jama karleta aur mujh ko koi takleef nah pahunchti. mein to mominon ko dar aur khushkhabri sunanay wala hon
  7,189,woh khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko 1 shakhs se pedakiya aur is se is ka jora banaya taakay is se raahat haasil kere. so jab woh is ke paas jata hai to usay halka sa hamal reh jata hai aur woh is ke sath chalti phurti hai. phir jab kuch boojh maloom karti yani bacha pait mein bara hota hai to dono miyan biwi apne perwar-digaar khuday-e azzwajal se iltija karte hain ke agar to hamein sahih o salim ( bacha ) day ga to hum tairay shukar guzar hon ge
  7,190,jab woh un ko sahih o salim ( bacha ) deta hai to is ( bachay ) mein jo woh un ko deta hai is ka shareek muqarrar karte hain. jo woh shirk karte hain ( khuda ka rutba ) is se buland hai
  7,191,kiya woh aison ko shareek banatay hain jo kuch bhi peda nahi kar saktay aur khud peda kiye jatay hain
  7,192,aur nah un ki madad ki taaqat rakhtay hain aur nah apni hi madad kar saktay hain
  7,193,agar tum un ko seedhay raste ki taraf bulaao to tumhara kaha nah manen. tumahray liye barabar hai ke tum un ko bulaao ya chupkay ho raho
  7,194,( mushrako ) jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho woh tumhari terhan ke bande hi hain ( acha ) tum un ko poukaro agar sachey ho to chahiye ke woh tum ko jawab bhi den
  7,195,bhala un ke paon hain jin se chalein ya haath hain jin se pakren ya ankhen hain jin se dekhen ya kaan hain jin se sunen? keh do ke apne sharikon ko bulalo aur mere baray mein ( jo ) tadbeer ( karni ho ) karlo aur mujhe kuch mohlat bhi nah do ( phir dekho ke woh merakiya kar saktay hain )
  7,196,mera madadgaar to khuda hi hai jis ne kitaab ( barhaq ) nazil ki. aur naik logon ka wohi Dostdar hai
  7,197,aur jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho woh nah tumhari hi madad ki taaqat rakhtay hain aur nah khud hi apni madad kar saktay hain
  7,198,aur agar tum un ko seedhay raste ki taraf bulaao to sun nah saken aur tum inhen dekhte ho ke ( bah zahir ) ankhen khole tumhari taraf dekh rahay hain magar ( fi al waqea ) kuch nahi dekhte
  7,199,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) Afoo ikhtiyar karo aur naik kaam karne ka hukum do aur jahilon se kinara karlo
  7,200,aur agar shetan ki taraf se tumahray dil mein kisi terhan ka waswasa peda ho to khuda se panah mango. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) sab kuch jan-nay wala hai
  7,201,jo log parhaizgaar hain jab un ko shetan ki taraf se koi waswasa peda hota hai to choank parte hain aur ( dil ki ankhen khol kar ) dekhnay lagtay hain
  7,202,aur un ( kufar ) ke bhai inhen gumraahi mein kheinchain jatay hain phir ( is mein kisi terhan ki ) kotahi nahi karte
  7,203,aur jab tum un ke paas ( kuch dinon taq ) koi aayat nahi laatay to kehte hain ke tum ne ( apni taraf se ) kyun nahi banali. keh do ke mein to isi ki pairwi karta hon jo mere perwar-digaar ki taraf se mere paas aata hai. yeh quran tumahray perwar-digaar ki janib se Danish -o- basirat aur mominon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  7,204,aur jab quran parha jaye to tavajja se suna karo aur khamosh raha karo taakay tum par rehamkiya jaye
  7,205,aur apne perwar-digaar ko dil hi dil mein aajzi aur khauf se aur pust aawaz se subah vsham yaad karte raho aur ( dekhna ) ghaafil nah hona
  7,206,jo log tumahray perwar-digaar ke paas hain woh is ki ibadat se gardan kashi nahi karte aur is pak zaat ko yaad karte aur is ke agay sjday karte rehtay hain
